				<td colspan="2"><span>I just did this a few weeks ago and what I did was go to sebelis, make sure the UDB was up, then start telling LFGs. I asked in guild first and got 1 person out of 20 or so to come who happened to be a mage. Also ask your friends but if you come up short on people start looking at the LFGs and asking. The worst that will happen is they will say no thanks and you try someone else.
